Defense wins championships! Check it out before you head into wrestling post season or your next BJJ practice!
“Bioavailable to humans”

Just hearing this song and was a little reminder to be grateful for all the laughs and giggles, screams and yells, messy floors and dirty faces, with my two little ladies (and Leo haha). We are always told it goes by fast but they don’t say how fast it will feel. Here is to many more adventures and many more laughs! Glad your mom and I can share this life with you!

Championship week coming up! 

Throwback to the college days with my friends, brothers, coaches, and family! 

My only advice to those competing is to compete your best and leave nothing left in the tank! @ncaawrestling @ncaa #marchmatness

p.s. I was trying to take Coach Spates' and Coach Koll's hands off their arms with those hand slaps haha
Time flys! Ten years ago @kyledake444 was getting ready to make history at the @ncaawrestling championships. Who will make history this weekend? 🧨
The semi finals are officially underway! 10 years ago @kyledake444 punched his ticket to his 4th final. Who you got going to the finals this year? 🧨

Ten years ago, @kyledake444 claimed his 4th national title and as we celebrate this milestone, it begs the question:
Who were the key players in your own journey towards success? 🧨

Really happy for my teammate, coach, and friend on his incredible season at the helm of my Alma mater! Incredible person and deserving of all his awards! Bringing home a team trophy is no easy task, and in his second season no less. Congratulations on everything and I’m excited to see what you will do next! Thanks again for everything along the way! #yellcornell @coach_mikegrey
Who should I use my vote for? I think I have a guy in mind! He did something I never did in the finals!!! #hodgetrophy

Leo turns 1 on the 10 year anniversary of me winning my 4th national title. Had no idea last year that it was the same day, but it is pretty cool! Happy Birthday buddy!

Edit: that’s cap I did know apparently but having 3 kids made me forget haha

Put a smile on! 

Pretty much sums up what I feel like waking up every morning knowing I am able to chase down my dreams and do what I love. Go chase down your dreams with a smile and be thankful for the opportunity to get up and go! It’s the little things that build up over time to make the big moments happen, so go get it!
2 more day until the Pan-Am championship’s 🧨
